                    <div class="appForm infoBlock">
                        <div class="welcomeSalutation">
                            <h4>Welcome to the Affirm Financial Credit Application!</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p>The application should take only 5-10 minutes to complete,
                            and you'll receive a response in as little as 30 seconds.</p>
                        <apex:pageMessages id="stepZeroPageMessages" />
                        <div>
                            <table id="szTbl">
                                <tr>
                                    <th width="50%" style="text-align: center;">What do I
                                        need?</th>
                                    <th width="50%" style="text-align: center;">What else
                                        should I know?</th>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>To complete this application you will need:
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Employment and Income Information</li>
                                            <li>Monthly expenses such as mortgage payments or rental
                                                payments</li>
                                            <li>Any other expense obligation you may have such as
                                                loan and credit card payments</li>
                                            <li>A SIN is optional but it can help in the application
                                                process</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </td>
                                    <td>Once your application is approved, we do require to
                                        ask a few personal questions based on your credit bureau
                                        history. The information you provide to us will be compared to
                                        your credit bureau file and will used to authenticate your
                                        identity. We require your authorization to check your credit
                                        bureau to complete this process and review your credit
                                        application.</td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <table id="ltTbl">
                                <td>Would you like to apply for:</td>
                                <td><apex:selectRadio id="loanTypeField"
